                                                                                               NIST SP 800-181 REV. 1                                    WORKFORCE FRAMEWORK FOR CYBERSECURITY
                                                                                                                                                                             (NICE FRAMEWORK)

                                                                                               Other organizations could use Competencies to determine whether a learner has achieved a
                                                                                               defined set of Skills and Knowledge. These organizations could, as depicted in Figure 3, choose
                                                                                               to use Competencies as groups of K&S statements. These organizations could then assess the
                                                                                               learners for these K&S statements. Assessments could take the form of tests, lab-based
                                                                                               demonstration, or oral evaluations.
